	(text "- Provide a stable 400 VDC bus for the power stage\n- Store energy to support load transients\n- Reduce DC bus voltage ripple\n- Work together with the pre‑charge circuit to limit inrush stress\n\nThe DC‑link is implemented as a parallel bank of electrolytic capacitors between DC+ and DC−\n\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 15.494 29.718 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.651 1.651)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "26badd5d-63ce-4d4e-8f58-c4983168e6f5")
	)
	(text "With f = 40k Hz, and I = {0.5A, 1.25A, 2A} you get the following"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 57.404 73.406 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.651 1.651)
			)
		)
		(uuid "c83ed6d8-17df-403b-8eec-34916663c6f9")
	)
	(text "This subsheet implements the bulk DC‑link energy storage for the inverter. Its purpose is to:"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 87.376 18.288 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.032 2.032)
			)
		)
		(uuid "cdf84ef9-8962-43c7-ac71-742f09df88af")
	)
	(text "On a 400 V bus, that's on the order of 0.01-0.05% ripple."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 54.102 98.298 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.651 1.651)
			)
		)
		(uuid "d55dff36-df22-4493-b92a-f958426327c9")
	)
	(text "The ripple depends on how much current you pull from the bus and at what \"ripple frequency\". The basic capacitor relation is:\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 96.774 40.386 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.651 1.651)
			)
		)
		(uuid "dc7f677a-1177-4c52-a4ce-3c0879f952e4")
	)
	(text_box "DC Link total of 220 uF in electrolytic caps, 10 uF in Film caps = 230 uF in total DC Link capacitance"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 134.62 66.294 0)
		(size 105.918 3.048)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
			(width 0)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
